headline: Celebrating 40 Years of the Nasdaq-100 Index® (NDX®)
summary: The combined value of all investment products tracking the NDX® ecosystem globally exceeds $500 billion 94 Exchange Traded Products track NDX® in over 20 countries across 6 continents NEW YORK, Jan. 31, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Nasdaq, Inc. (Nasdaq: NDAQ) proudly marks the 40th anniversary of the Nasdaq-100 Index® (NDX®), the world’s preeminent large-cap growth benchmark. Since its inception on January 31, 1985, the index has redefined innovation and transformed the global investment landscape.
